'''Clipper''', named also "Clipper '''BENELUX'''", was the company that distributed Star Wars [[Kenner Products|Kenner]] toys in Belgium ('''BE'''lgium), Holland ('''NE'''therlands) and Luxembourg ('''LUX'''embourg) in the vintage era.

